[00:00.00]I: Hello, there!
[00:00.00]J: I beg your pardon?
[00:00.00]I: Hello! How are you getting on?
[00:00.00]J: Fine, thank you . . . sorry . . . do I know you?
[00:00.00]I: Yes, it’s me, Nick Fowler!
[00:00.00]J: Sorry, I don’t think I know you.
[00:00.00]I: Aren’t you Harry Shiner?
[00:00.00]J: Er, no . . . I’m afraid not.
[00:00.00]I: Oh, I’m terribly sorry, I thought you were someone else!
